{"title":"果园板话","authors":["冯福和"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"果园板话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河北交河秦村人民公社社员　冯福和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云高风清八月天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取经藁城百果园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫槐杨柳夹长道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃杏梨林像棋盘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架上葡萄蔽天日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"畦中树苗拂人肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过条条幼林带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梨树丛里见水潭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潭水碧透细浪翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪里鱼影银光闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林中少年指相告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是八一自流泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八一池面六七亩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两次放鱼四五万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三九时节不结冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十冬腊月像春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐看太阳向西沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听隔岸竹板声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老头背筐唱着走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腔调洪亮字眼清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年遥指老汉影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快板大王王老景！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十三岁不服老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时不唱也不行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员叫他留声机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自称是个广播筒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年讨饭学过唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会唱时调几百种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月刚到果园来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬老院里挂个名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿坐吃现成饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃杏林中作零工。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃杏节过老人闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兔场来当饲养员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天打草四五筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论晴天和阴天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满怀钦敬求相见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年领到兔场边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿荫丛中静悄悄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一见如故老人欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银白胡子红润脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健步挺胸开笑颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝布短褂土黄裤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张口先提“俺果园”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人鼓掌求听歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人掏出毛竹板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭身退步点点头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叽哩呱撻响一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声调圆滑开唱腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字句稳重不慌忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹板声停掌声起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐声欢请往下唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人低头略思索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹板继续响叮当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱段社员战沙荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱段千亩葡萄方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱词滔滔哗哗响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大锤砸破荷花缸？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹板呱呱上下翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指头扳开机关枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人越唱脸越红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人越听越想听。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹板忽停唱声止，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里果园寂无声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人众人心相融，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树下围坐叙家常。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起当年辛酸事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉流下泪两行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家住沙沟李贵庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三亩洼地间半房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糠粃干菜半年粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草根树叶常吃光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风起处流沙卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗枯草净路荒凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋季连年闹山水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打捞残穗喝沙汤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五岁上扛长活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛马同住十六春；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十三岁娶媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又给地主去看坟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坟场角上挖地窨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半阴半阳半像坟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天常和牛作伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜只跟鬼为邻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生下三女和一子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒野地里长成人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"财主上坟扔剩果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家拾来和泪吞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风猖獗沙石滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天昏地暗阴森森。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄沙堵塞地窨口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿急外出难开门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏雨连绵湿淋淋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窨里积水一尺深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炕塌被烂夜难睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无柴无米吃菜根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋夜蟋蟀声纷纷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒野虫鸣最惊心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"财主庭院赏明月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人荒郊伴野魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬雪飘飘漫孤坟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四望茫茫不见人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"财主围炉饮暖酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷儿卧冰冻裂唇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人看守财主坟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按时清扫祭亡魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自家祖坟断香火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人死后作穷魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夫妻只叹福禄薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家跟着受折磨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿病床头没钱治，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘?儿死无奈何。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军阀混战逃兵多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜兵匪坟场过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯进小屋搜财物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得老伴皮肉破。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个女儿惊吓死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一女受惊成疯魔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此不敢住坟场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍痛辞了财主活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶妻抱女找破庙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结交几个花儿哥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会唱曲数快板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿门讨饭度生活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人声音渐细慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两行热泪洒胸前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着竹板手发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"递给众人仔细看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小竹板三寸宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头挂着古铜钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里外油亮黄褐色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知打了多少年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人手指毛竹板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口角发抖又开言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“此物伴我三十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时也没离身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年全家遭了难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头卖唱在晋县。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏这块小竹板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲些残汤和剩饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风揭破瓦露星天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头古庙是家园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里悲酸嘴里唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔苦楚对谁言？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从来了八路军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村穷人大翻身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分了房子又分地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到老家李贵村。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争会上竹板响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出心头多年恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒地主和恶霸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此不作流浪人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业实现合作化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民欢庆拔穷根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福路上迈大步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹板一敲添精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线照亮乾坤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社化高潮到俺村。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福大路更宽广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹板越敲越有劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老来公社是靠山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里感激口难言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几次请求高主任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批准来当饲养员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果园建设才一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙荒面貌大改变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗圃幼树千万棵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地挖出自流泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西瓜长的水筲大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄累累蜜样甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴吃葡萄心里美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心想公社脸上欢。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人擦净满脸泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻打竹板又开言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光冲散千层雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"福星永照百果园。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}